name: The Winning Days
description: The pilot and his co-pilot have accepted their fate. Stranded in a god-forsaken planet away from their homeworld. Hoping for a chance that somebody would receive the distress signal from their emergency beacon attached to their mech before the reserve battery runs out completely. The giant mech has seen its days, now sits immobilized, at the mercy of the scorching sun that burns anything exposed to its ray.
